Frosty the Snowman (Ultimate Christmas Classics)


One of the great holiday classics that we all grew up watching. 

The story is simple: A magic hat brings &quot;Frosty&quot; the snowman to life, after which he must travel to the North Pole to prevent being melted. Meanwhile, an evil magician is trying to redeem the hat for his own nefarious purposes.

For 42 years, this has been among the dearest of Christmas specials and will likely remain so for years to come.

Runtime: 27 mins
Language: English
Year: 1998
Quality: 9/10
